{"h994654ccgc846g420dgbb81g1c218e07c8f3": ["I've seen so little of the world. Still, there's time now.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Generics\\GLO_WorldGlobe_B_PAD.html", "a33d2f0d-5a9d-47b3-9a14-209c211aa87a"], "h2d9db046gc591g4b13g87a3g3d5ac63547c2": ["All these lands, oceans, empires. I'll see them all myself one day.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Generics\\GLO_WorldGlobe_B_PAD.html", "a33d2f0d-5a9d-47b3-9a14-209c211aa87a"], "h2820318dgc24dg4111gadd2ge7d00bb39d11": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Generics\\GLO_WorldGlobe_B_PAD.html", "a33d2f0d-5a9d-47b3-9a14-209c211aa87a"], "hce900e8bgac7eg47c2g8997gb2393bde4de2": ["|Karla : where I'm yet to travel? Globe B|", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Generics\\GLO_WorldGlobe_B_PAD.html", "a33d2f0d-5a9d-47b3-9a14-209c211aa87a"], "h845db456g7c60g4052g9b37g599f713a0336": ["My Varsh spoke bitterly of Toril. 'Harmless to a fault', she said.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Generics\\GLO_WorldGlobe_B_PAD.html", "a33d2f0d-5a9d-47b3-9a14-209c211aa87a"], "h58dd3afdg3567g473dgaaa6g8138373b4c77": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Generics\\GLO_WorldGlobe_B_PAD.html", "a33d2f0d-5a9d-47b3-9a14-209c211aa87a"], "h87e7fc9fge768g4c09g9dfbg72cb78967aa3": ["Toril. I wonder if anyone's ever circled it the whole way around.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Generics\\GLO_WorldGlobe_B_PAD.html", "a33d2f0d-5a9d-47b3-9a14-209c211aa87a"], "h7d3f4c19g90aeg4534g9542gdcb1c3e9c709": ["A whole world there for the exploring.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Generics\\GLO_WorldGlobe_B_PAD.html", "a33d2f0d-5a9d-47b3-9a14-209c211aa87a"], "h96dac104ge25ag4e9fg8ef0gbf0abd7bd81a": ["Such a small world. Do they even know of the planes?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Generics\\GLO_WorldGlobe_B_PAD.html", "a33d2f0d-5a9d-47b3-9